data.description: Welcome to 606 Shady Avenue - a spacious 3-bedroom, 2-full-bath home that's move-in ready. This welcoming residence features a large eat-in kitchen, a formal dining room, and a generously sized living room. Plus, the convenience of first-floor laundry makes chores a breeze.    Step outside to experience the outdoor charm – relax on the front patio or take in the view from the deck. Plus, with a 2-car detached garage, parking is a breeze.
